AI-Driven Features Comparison
Personalization Depth

TSP Solver: Highest - Multi-dimensional user behavior analysis
Cycle Detection: Medium - Graph pattern recognition and algorithm selection
Median Finder: Medium - Stream pattern analysis and optimization mode selection

Adaptation Speed

Median Finder: Fastest - Real-time optimization mode switching
Cycle Detection: Medium - Algorithm selection based on graph characteristics
TSP Solver: Gradual - Learns from multiple problem instances

